  // Social: "Your phone already has dozens of features that can change your life — bigger text, voice commands, a magnifying glass, live captions, and hearing aid support. They're FREE. They're already installed. And most people have no idea they exist. Here's the tour every iPhone and Android owner should take."
  // Newsletter: "Your phone cost a lot of money. And it came loaded with powerful tools that Apple and Google mostly keep buried in their Settings menus. These aren't gimmicks — they're life-changing features for anyone whose eyes are not what they used to be, whose ears could use a little help, or whose hands shake a bit when typing. Best of all, they are completely free, already on your device, and take about five minutes each to turn on. This guide walks through the ones that matter most, in plain English, with the exact settings path for both iPhone and Android."
